# Bulls & Cows — Improvement Plan

Use this plan when adding features or refactoring. Prioritize small, shippable slices.

## Current State

- **Stack**: Expo SDK 55, React Native, TypeScript
- **Game model**: 9 innings, 3 outs per inning, 3-digit unique secret, baseball-themed scoring
- **Core logic**: `src/lib/game.ts`, `src/lib/inning.ts`, state in `src/hooks/useGame.ts`
- **UI**: `src/screens/`, `src/components/`, `src/theme/`
- **Stats**: `src/hooks/useStats.ts`, persisted via AsyncStorage
- **i18n**: `src/i18n/` (KO default, EN), `react-i18next` + AsyncStorage language pref

---

## Phase 1 — Quick Wins (Logic + UX)

### Logic

- [x] **Disable Enter until guess is complete** — `submitGuess` already validates; disable the Enter key and show helper text when `currentGuess.length < DIGIT_COUNT`.
- [x] **Gray out used digits on keypad** — pass `currentGuess` into keypad; dim keys whose digit is already entered (duplicate prevention is silent today).
- [x] **Block input during sound/modal transitions** — `inningEndVisible` / `gameEndVisible` already gate input; also disable keypad while `playCallSequence` is in flight to avoid double-submit.
- [x] **Sync README with actual rules** — document innings, outs, and run scoring; remove the 10-attempt limit.

### UI

- [x] **Per-digit feedback in attempt history** — color each digit in `AttemptRow`: green = strike, yellow = ball, gray = out (reuse strike-position logic from guess boxes).
- [x] **Shake or pulse on invalid submit** — brief animation on guess boxes when validation fails (replace or supplement `Alert`).
- [x] **Perfect-game celebration** — when `inningResults.filter(r => r.scored).length === TOTAL_INNINGS`, show distinct copy/emoji on game-end modal.
- [x] **Settings toggles** — sound on/off, haptics on/off (persist with `AsyncStorage`).

