## Phase 2 — Structure & Reliability

### Logic

- [x] **Unit tests for `game.ts`** — cover `scoreGuess`, `isValidGuessDigits`, `generateSecretDigits` (uniqueness, range, edge cases like all-outs guess).
- [x] **Extract pure inning reducer** — move inning transitions (`submitGuess` outcome → next state) into testable functions in `src/lib/game.ts` or `src/lib/inning.ts`.
- [x] **High-score / stats persistence** — best run total, perfect games count, average attempts per scored inning.
- [x] **Undo last guess (optional)** — allow one undo per inning before next submit; clears last attempt and recalculates outs.

### UI / Architecture

- [x] **Split `App.tsx`** into:
  - `src/screens/HomeScreen.tsx`
  - `src/screens/GameScreen.tsx`
  - `src/components/` — `Pill`, `Keypad`, `GuessBoxes`, `AttemptRow`, `InningScoreboard`, `GameModal`
  - `src/theme/` — shared colors, spacing, typography (replace magic hex values)
- [x] **Remove dead code** — unused `playOneShot` in `useSound.ts`, unused styles (`hero`, `howtoContent`, `secretHintArea`, etc.).

### i18n & Settings UI

- [x] **KO/EN i18n** — full app copy in `src/i18n/locales/`; default language KO.
- [x] **Language chip picker** — KO / EN chip buttons in Settings card (`LanguageSettingsRow`).
- [x] **Standard switch rows** — sound effect and haptic feedback use label + switch only (no Off/On flanking labels).

