## Phase 3 — Polish & Accessibility

### Logic

- [x] **Configurable difficulty** — optional 4-digit mode or fewer innings (constants in `src/constants/game.ts`).
- [x] **Hint system** — after N failed attempts in an inning, reveal one digit position (limit hints per inning).

### UI

- [x] **Animations** — `LayoutAnimation` or Reanimated for attempt list insert, out-dot fill, modal enter.
- [x] **Accessibility** — `accessibilityLabel` on keypad and guess boxes; announce S/B/O results via `AccessibilityInfo.announceForAccessibility`.
- [x] **Dark mode** — theme tokens + `useColorScheme`; StatusBar follows scheme.
- [x] **Responsive layout** — constrain max width on tablets; optional landscape scoreboard sidebar.
- [x] **Onboarding** — first-launch tooltip or collapsible “How to play” on game screen.

